{"_path":"/councilor/service/s2046","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"質詢 - 加速打通長慶一街, 樂善一路","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s2046-1.jpeg","sequence":2046,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/18c22mvB55/","author":"李宗豪","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"李宗豪"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-12-11T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"質詢-加速打通長慶一街-樂善一路"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"質詢 - 加速打通長慶一街, 樂善一路"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這二日準時議會報到，補上先前颱風假沒質詢到的局處，今日質詢都發局，也跟大家報告相關進度："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n1、長慶一街打通"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n「長慶一街打通至長慶三街」都市計畫已通過，目前在進行用地取得，宗豪要求加速進度，副市長承諾會積極與長庚醫院協調土地取得，加速道路開闢。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n2、樂善一路打通"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n工務局道路規劃草案已經完成，於 11 月舉辦公展前說明會，目前正在準備變更都市計畫，我要求都發局變更進度要加快，未來樂善一路打通後，變一銜接變二，才能完善聯外路網，讓居民更加便利。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2046-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2046-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"質詢-加速打通長慶一街-樂善一路","depth":2,"text":"質詢 - 加速打通長慶一街, 樂善一路"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s2046.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s2046.md","_extension":"md"}